the story of g.i. joe is a 1945 american comedy film directed by george sherman and starring robert mitchum , robert mitchum , and robert mitchum . the film is based on the novel of g.i. joe : the rise of g.i. joe , the film is about a man who returns to the united states . the film was released by warner bros. on march 13 , 1945 . the film was released on november 4 , 1945 , by united artists .